|GKB-- Druid Monitor ----------------------------------------------|000

|CKBdmon|000 toggles a compact nwyfre monitor in your normal combat
monitor output.

Commands:

  |CKBdmon        |000 Toggle the Druid monitor.
  |CKBdmon on     |000 Turn it on.
  |CKBdmon off    |000 Turn it off.

When enabled, the standard |CKBmon|000 / |CKBmonitor|000 output includes
one extra line with all four currents:

  T  Tellurian
  D  Daloan
  M  Marken
  K  Tekali

Each current shows a compact bar and percentage so you can see which
vessel is being spent during combat.
